content:
Launch an LWC OmniScript with LWC OmniScript Wrapper

Available beginning with Vlocity Insurance and Health Winter '20, and CME Winter '20.

Deploy an LWC OmniScript to make it available in Experience and Lightning App Builders. Review options for launching from a Lightning or Experience Page. See Activate and Deploy an LWC OmniScript and Launch LWC OmniScripts from Lightning and Experience Pages.

The wrapper component makes the OmniScript URL addressable, enabling parameter passing to the OmniScript. The Vlocity LWC OmniScript Wrapper component wraps an OmniScript to make it URL addressable.

If the LWC OmniScript Wrapper exists on a record page, the record ID passes into the OmniScript as Context ID automatically.

Launch LWC OmniScripts from Communities using URLs, Lightning pages, and layout actions. Make an OmniScript URL addressable with vlocityLWCOmniWrapper.
title: Deploying and Launching LWC OmniScripts
